<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reset Your Password</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* Global styles and link color fixes */
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f9fc;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        /* Fix for all link colors */
        a {
            color: #ff4081;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        /* Fix for button class to ensure white text */
        .button {
            color: white !important;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .button:visited, 
        .button:hover, 
        .button:active, 
        .button:focus {
            color: white !important;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            background: #ffffff;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 0;
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
            overflow: hidden; /* Keep content inside rounded corners */
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff4081, #ff79a7);
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: url('https://res.cloudinary.com/ddqioccgt/image/upload/v1740635000/myqcm_pattern.png');
            opacity: 0.1;
            z-index: 0;
        }
        .header img {
            max-width: 140px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 35px;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #333;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .content h2 {
            font-size: 28px;
            color: #ff4081;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .content p {
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 14px 32px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff4081, #ff79a7);
            color: white !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 64, 129, 0.2);
        }
        .button:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff2d75, #ff6699);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(255, 64, 129, 0.25);
        }
        .info-box {
            background-color: #f9f5ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #ff4081;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: left;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .info-box p {
            margin: 0;
            color: #333;
            font-size: 15px;
        }
        .divider {
            height: 1px;
            background-color: #eee;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #888;
            padding: 20px 35px 30px;
            background-color: #f9fafc;
            border-radius: 0 0 16px 16px;
        }
        .social-icons {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .social-icons a {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 0 8px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        .social-icons a:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }
        .social-icons img {
            width: 28px;
            height: 28px;
            opacity: 0.85;
        }
        .contact-info {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #999;
        }
        .contact-info a {
            color: #ff4081;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        @media only screen and (max-width: 480px) {
            .container {
                margin: 10px;
            }
            .content {
                padding: 25px 20px;
            }
            .button {
                padding: 12px 24px;
                font-size: 15px;
                display: block;
                margin: 20px auto;
                max-width: 80%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dgxaezwuv/image/upload/v1748615201/MyQCM_logo_zxe7yu_dysxal.png" alt="MyQCM Logo">
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Reset Your Password</h2>
            <p>Hi <%= name %>,</p>
            <p>We received a request to reset your password for your MyQCM account , If you didn't request a password reset, please ignore this email or contact support if you have concerns.</p>
            
            <div class="info-box">
                <p><strong>Important:</strong> This link is valid for 10 minutes .</p>
            </div>

            <a href="<%= reset_url %>" class="button">Reset Password</a>
            
            
            <p>For security reasons, this password reset link can only be used once.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2025 MyQCM Aljazayr | All rights reserved.</p>
            <div class="social-icons">
                <a href="#"><img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/733/733547.png" alt="Facebook"></a>
                <a href="#"><img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/733/733579.png" alt="Twitter"></a>
                <a href="#"><img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/2111/2111463.png" alt="Instagram"></a>
                <a href="#"><img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/174/174857.png" alt="LinkedIn"></a>
            </div>
            <div class="contact-info">
                <p>Need help? Contact us at <a href="mailto:support@myqcmdz.com">support@myqcmdz.com</a></p>
                <p>You're receiving this email because a password reset was requested for your account.</p>
                <p><a href="{{privacyPolicyLink}}">Privacy Policy</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
